# CaseCrafted

Welcome to **CaseCrafted**! Your phone, your style, crafted to perfection. This repository contains the source code for the **CaseCrafted** website, showcasing a collection of stylish, functional, and customizable phone cases that reflect individuality.

## Table of Contents
- [About](#about)
- [Features](#features)
- [Demo](#demo)
- [Installation](#installation)
- [Usage](#usage)
- [Folder Structure](#folder-structure)
- [Technologies Used](#technologies-used)
- [Contributing](#contributing)
- [License](#license)

## About

At **CaseCrafted**, we believe that a phone is more than just a device. It’s an extension of who you are. Our mission is to design and craft phone cases that reflect your personal identity and provide reliable protection with a unique style. 

This website is built to showcase our products and allow users to learn more about what we offer.

## Features

- **Customizable Phone Cases**: Display a collection of customizable and stylish phone cases.
- **Responsive Design**: The website is fully responsive and works across all devices.
- **Dynamic Products Page**: Products are dynamically loaded from the assets folder (excluding the logo).
- **Simple and Modern Design**: Easy to navigate and visually appealing design.

## Demo

You can view the live version of the site here: [CaseCrafted GitHub Pages](https://casecrafted.github.io/casecrafted/)

